  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And as they say, that I'm a member of the community.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "End of story.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "They come and go, yes.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I still am contacted by them, yes.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] It's a strange relationship because they-- they recognize me as a member of the community, although I'm Jewish, although I'm married, I have nothing to do.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I'm part of their--",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The old ones, obviously, Roman.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never mind, after so many years, they still persist calling me that.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Actually, the-- one group of the monks, who was with me in the Carpathian mountains, later on found its way to Canada, to Woodstock, Ontario, and they lived there.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I visited them there.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I keep m-- very close contact with this church, with the bishops and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they know of me, and occasionally, I'm participate-- I'm asking to participate in programs to commemorate the Metropolitan, yes.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Which I do with pleasure.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I am always happy to testify to the greatness of the man, his assistance, his humanity, and his values.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] Jews in Poland considered him, if you know the expression, [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's right.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Very much so.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he says he has two heritages.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 75,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he has very close relationship with my brothers-- with his brothers.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 76,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Sorry.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Accident.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] Second point, I was very close to Belzitz, so I saw the destruction of the community, or the process of destruction of community at a very early stage.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I realized that we all carry a death sentence because of the place I was and knowledge of the topography.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 77,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Three, [PAUSES FOR 5 SECONDS] I was, probably since childhood, more aggressive and more enterprising-- aggressive not in a negative sense.",
      "word_count": 21
    }
  ],
